OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with some occasional
OL,6,Frain or drizzle this morning, mainly
OL,7,Facross the north. Otherwise a dry day
OL,8,Fwith some brightness breaking through
OL,9,Fthis afternoon. Warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,12,Flate brightness. Otherwise becoming
OL,13,Fcloudy overnight with some light and
OL,14,Fpatchy rain developing across the
OL,15,Fnorth and west at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FCloudy in the morning with a
OL,18,Flittle drizzly rain in the north. Dry
OL,19,Fin the afternoon with some warm
OL,20,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
